DepositCollateralTest
├── when token is not allowed
│   └── it should revert
└── when token is allowed
    ├── when amount is zero
    │   └── it should revert
    └── when amount is greater than zero
        ├── when transfer fails
        │   └── it should revert
        └── when transfer succeeds
            ├── it should record the deposited collateral
            ├── it should emit CollateralDeposited event
            └── it should transfer tokens to the engine
